    \section{Professional Summary}
    
    \begin{onecolentry}
    Certified Ethical Hacker (\textbf{C|EH}) with \textbf{1 year} of practical experience in \textit{Red and Blue Team operations}. Skilled in \textbf{VAPT} across \textit{Web, Cloud, API, Mobile,} and \textit{Network} environments. Experienced in \textit{Purple Team} collaboration, \textbf{SIEM (Wazuh)}, and \textbf{EDR (ThreatSpike)} management for \textit{threat detection} and \textit{incident response}. Well-versed in global standards such as \textit{ISO 27001}, \textit{SOC 2}, \textit{NIST 800-53}, and \textit{GDPR}. Focused on strengthening security posture through effective \textbf{detection}, \textbf{response}, and \textbf{defense}.
    \end{onecolentry}
    
