    \section*{Professional Experience}
    
    \textbf{Cyber Security Analyst – Full-time} \\
    Cybrotech Digiventure Pvt. Ltd., New Delhi \hfill Jan 2025 – Present \\
    \href{https://cybrotech.us}{cybrotech.us}
    \begin{itemize}[leftmargin=*]
        \item Conducted red teaming assessments simulating realistic attack scenarios to evaluate client defenses and improve detection and response capabilities.
    
        \item Maintained Wazuh SIEM infrastructure in production, processing high-volume logs with near 100\% uptime; developed custom detection rules mitigating 12 confirmed incidents including DDoS, brute-force, and MITM attacks.
    
        \item Conducted and supported 12+ client VAPT projects identifying numerous vulnerabilities (including CVEs, EJS injection, IDOR, WordPress flaws), providing remediation plans that reduced client risk exposure by 40\%.
    
        \item Deployed ISO/IEC 27001:2022 aligned controls and configured systems for SOC 2, NIST, GDPR, and TSC for CIS compliance, achieving audit readiness and regulatory adherence for multiple clients.
    
        \item Automated compliance workflows through SIEM integrations, significantly reducing time required for audit preparation and reporting.
    
        \item Delivered cybersecurity awareness training programs to 7+ SMB clients, driving adoption of security best practices and reducing phishing susceptibility by 80\%.
    
        \item Authored standardized playbooks for client onboarding and incident response, improving consistency and efficiency across security operations.
    
        \item Regularly prepared and delivered detailed security incident and vulnerability reports to client SOC centers, enabling timely response and continuous security improvements.
    
    \end{itemize}
    
